        {
            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23019147?u=4c0de81596ced64dc067dea5686f7ca2912db0cb&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Description</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">The <code class=\"notranslate\">fullscreen</code> and <code class=\"notranslate\">picture-in-picture</code> values of the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media/display-mode#syntax\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code class=\"notranslate\">display-mode</code></a> media feature currently link to their respective API pages.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">These links should be updated to point to the correct values of the <code class=\"notranslate\">display-mode</code> media feature.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Motivation</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Update links to point to the correct information</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Related issues and pull requests</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Related PR about the <code class=\"notranslate\">display</code> manifest: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2371040699\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/34386\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/mdn/content/pull/34386/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/pull/34386\">#34386</a></p>",
            "url": "https://github.com/mdn/content/pull/34387",
            "title": "fix(css): Fix the `display-mode` links in the `@media` feature",
