            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5368500?v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/><p dir=\"auto\">FF111 renamed the <code class=\"notranslate\">options.imageOrientation</code> parameter value passed to <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code class=\"notranslate\">createImageBitmap()</code></a> from <code class=\"notranslate\">none</code> to <code class=\"notranslate\">from-image</code>. This just adds a release note.<br>\nRelated docs work can be tracked in <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1529819995\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/23564\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/mdn/content/issues/23564/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/23564\">#23564</a></p>",
